Package org.netbeans.modules.uihandler.api

Package with interfaces that other modules may implement in order to be notified about important lifecycle points during collecting the UI Gestures.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Activated
    Shall be registered in Lookup.getDefault() and is then called when the UI logger module is activated.
    Deactivated
    Shall be registered in Lookup.getDefault() and is then called when the UI logger module is about to produce results.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Class that allows other modules to control the behavior of the UI Gestures submit process.

Package org.netbeans.modules.uihandler.api Description

Package with interfaces that other modules may implement in order to be notified about important lifecycle points during collecting the UI Gestures.
